                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18400817-2147-offence-1 t18400817-cd-206"></join>15th of August</rs>, 3 loaves of bread, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., and 1 3/4lbs. weight of flour, value 5<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18400817-name-1253" type="victimName">
